title: New: Laura Welsh – Unravel
content:
Jessie Ware happened, the world got pretty excited, so it stands to reason that musicians are going to want to replicate such a sound.

Laura Welsh’s new cut, Unravel, takes her style and runs with it, not exactly into unconquered territory, but at least into a space that showcases her range, which as it happens could be pretty exciting. Oh and Dev Hynes produced the track, which is probably why you’ve already heard it.

Hut play or D/L below.
